reviews.text:
This stuff is amazeballs. Sure, it's what it says on the tin: a thin mint frappuccino...but it's soooo much more. The chocolate is rich and dark. The mint is decadent as all get out, and the coffee...it's nice and strong, but not overpowering. This stuff is so good, i wrecked my 30 ml inside of 4 days (which is a record for me), and I kept scorching the cotton because it's so tasty, i'd keep hitting it until "oh, hell."&#xD;
&#xD;
Two quick questions: Did you get these cookies off the girl scouts Wednesday Addams jacked?&#xD;
&#xD;
and more importantly:&#xD;
&#xD;
How in the name of all that is holy am i the first one to review this?!?&#xD;
&#xD;
Sublime stuff, man.
